WEBVTT

00:05.750 --> 00:08.380
天啊  什么都没有
God. Nothing. It's dead.

00:09.960 --> 00:12.170
他们就要弄清楚了
They're figuring it out.

00:13.260 --> 00:15.470
这是种什么样的炸药
What kind of explosives are we talking about?

00:15.640 --> 00:16.760
自制炸药
Little home brew.

00:16.930 --> 00:19.310
迈克说它能释放出C4塑胶炸药
Michael says it has the energy release of C4.

00:19.470 --> 00:22.140
再试一次
Run the diagnostic again.

00:23.440 --> 00:25.230
快试
Run it.

00:25.850 --> 00:26.980
都是C4吗
Almost C4?

00:30.610 --> 00:32.190
是的
This is it.

00:32.360 --> 00:35.450
我们最后的机会  愿上帝保佑
Last chance for everybody.And we're gonna need a little luck.

00:38.370 --> 00:40.950
要是我出了什么事
If anything happens to me...

00:41.450 --> 00:44.080
务必让L.J.和索菲... ...
...make sure L.J. and Sofia....

00:45.040 --> 00:46.080
明白
You got it.

00:46.250 --> 00:48.210
-我也一样  -是的
-Same for me? -Yeah.

00:48.380 --> 00:50.750
低头  我们开始
Yeah, put your head down, let's go.

00:50.920 --> 00:52.550
开始
Let's go.

01:05.940 --> 01:09.650
随着时间的流逝
You know, someday,weeks will go by. Maybe even years.

01:09.820 --> 01:12.020
我们会淡忘这些事
It won't even cross our minds.

01:12.190 --> 01:14.150
只要我们活下去
Yeah, all we gotta do is survive.

01:14.990 --> 01:16.280
我们会的
We will.

01:17.070 --> 01:18.820
我保证
Promise.

01:24.160 --> 01:25.330
-发生什么事了  -没反应
-What happened? -Nothing.

01:25.500 --> 01:27.040
引爆器一定失灵了
The detonator must have failed.

01:27.210 --> 01:29.750
拖住他们  我们五分钟后到
Distract them. We'll be there in five minutes.

01:29.920 --> 01:33.630
-我们没有时间了  -那你必须手动引爆
-No, we don't have five seconds. -Then you'll have to trigger it manually.

01:34.760 --> 01:36.800
我有多少时间
How much time is that gonna give me?

01:39.760 --> 01:41.800
滚出来  马上
Out. Now.

01:44.100 --> 01:45.850
阿历克斯
Alex?

01:46.810 --> 01:48.270
阿历克斯
Alex?

01:48.440 --> 01:50.650
这里面什么都没有
It's wiped clean.

01:50.810 --> 01:52.900
-不可能  -真的吗
-That's not possible.-Really?

01:53.070 --> 01:57.070
-那它在哪  数据在哪  -我拿的时候还好好的
-Then where is it? Where is the data? -It was intact when I took it.

01:57.400 --> 01:58.490
听着
I'll tell you what.

01:58.660 --> 02:00.700
如果它10秒钟内没反应
It doesn't boot up in 10 seconds...

02:00.870 --> 02:03.700
我会让你脑浆迸发
...I'm gonna splatter your skull all over these walls.

02:03.870 --> 02:05.830
是我来主动找的你
I came to you.

02:06.000 --> 02:08.210
我想结束这一切  我不会陷自己于不义
I want this over, I wouldn’t jeopardize that.

02:10.830 --> 02:13.710
我不相信迈克就这么让你拿走
I don't believe that Michael just let you have it.

02:14.340 --> 02:17.630
他没有  趁他不在时我拿的
He didn't. He left me alone in a room and I took it.

02:18.220 --> 02:21.390
他就一点没怀疑你
And that wasn't the least bit suspicious to you?

02:21.550 --> 02:23.470
也许吧  我
Maybe, I--

02:24.640 --> 02:25.770
我不知道
I don't know.

02:27.310 --> 02:29.390
你是在耍我吧
Are you lying?

02:32.360 --> 02:33.650
杀了他
Kill the junkie.

