《越狱》第四季 第二十二集
Prison.Break.S04E22

03:26.660 --> 03:28.580
你呼吸困难  是不是很痛
Your breathing's short? Does it hurt?

03:28.750 --> 03:31.330
-我还好  -你好像是肺部虚脱
-I'm fine.-Like hell, you collapsed your lung.

03:31.500 --> 03:33.580
不去医院  那跟去监狱没啥区别
No hospitals. Hospitals mean jail.

03:33.750 --> 03:35.170
快点  快点
Come on, come on.

03:35.290 --> 03:38.550
-你能帮他治疗吗  -要先检查检查再说
-Can you treat him?-I need a better look before I can try.

03:38.710 --> 03:40.010
克里斯蒂娜呢
Christina?

03:41.220 --> 03:42.800
死了
Buried.

03:54.100 --> 03:57.360
你个废物
Ugh! You pathetic slug.

03:57.520 --> 04:00.150
莎拉是我们的唯一筹码
Sara was the only leverage we had.

04:00.280 --> 04:04.030
斯科菲尔德是个全才  可啥时候成蜘蛛侠了
Scofield's donned many a chapeau, but human fly?

04:04.200 --> 04:07.240
我哪知道他会飞檐走壁
I should anticipate him scaling the building?

04:07.410 --> 04:11.000
布饶发  给我枪
Move on Panama. Broffer, your .9.

04:17.920 --> 04:20.840
巴格威尔  为我卖命的人
Men in my employ, Bagwell...

04:21.170 --> 04:22.550
要履行职责
...anticipate.

04:23.760 --> 04:26.260
尽忠职守
They cover their bases.

04:26.430 --> 04:27.640
他们都能完成任务
They refuse to fail...

04:27.800 --> 04:31.810
但你却一事无成
...which you seem to do with unyielding consistency.

04:35.560 --> 04:37.270
莎拉的手机
That's gotta be Sara's phone.

04:37.440 --> 04:38.940
我必须接
I should answer it.

04:39.940 --> 04:41.690
将军  你不会有什么损失的
What do you got to lose, general?

04:44.700 --> 04:46.160
喂
Hello.

04:46.280 --> 04:47.620
谁
Who the hell is this?

04:47.780 --> 04:50.580
是费尔南多·苏克雷吗  谢天谢地
Is this Fernando Sucre? Oh, thank you, God.

04:50.740 --> 04:52.620
-巴格威尔
-Bagwell?

04:52.790 --> 04:55.830
我们是一条船上的  一条船
And we're on the same team, brother. Same team.

04:56.000 --> 04:58.380
我正处于水深火热中  
The old boy's in a hell of a pickle.

04:58.540 --> 04:59.590
迈克在哪
Where's Michael?

05:01.170 --> 05:04.630
他妈妈抓走了他还有唐克雷蒂跟林肯
Uh, his mother snatched him and Tancredi, Linc too.

05:04.800 --> 05:07.550
而我吃了一记闷棍
And I, personally, took a nasty beat down.

05:07.720 --> 05:11.010
-她把他们关哪了  -我知道  但不能在电话里说
-Where does she have them? -I got an idea, I can't say on the phone.

05:11.180 --> 05:12.310
我得小心点  朋友
I'm running scared, amigo.

05:12.470 --> 05:14.560
冷静
Okay, cool it, you know what?

05:14.730 --> 05:17.940
我们找到个人能帮我们  但我要找到迈克
We got somebody who can help us but I need to get ahold of Michael.

05:18.110 --> 05:20.610
我们应该碰碰头  通通信息
We should, uh, get together and pool our resources.

05:20.770 --> 05:23.610
72大街的公园  1小时后见
The park on 72nd Avenue. Uh, in an hour.

05:26.030 --> 05:29.160
-好  马上到  -太好了
-Okay, I'll be there. -Excellent, perfecto.

05:30.700 --> 05:33.410
你找到能帮忙的人了
You got someone who can help on his cause.

05:33.580 --> 05:35.750
我相信他能引出斯科菲尔德
I'm certain he can draw out Scofield.

05:35.910 --> 05:37.920
你相信个屁
You're certain of nothing.

05:38.080 --> 05:41.460
但我一小时后要跟斯科菲尔德的朋友见面
Yet I do have a sit-down with Scofield's friend in an hour.

05:41.630 --> 05:43.460
将军  你没有更好的办法了
You got no better hand, general.

05:46.430 --> 05:47.680
跟着他去
Go with him.

05:48.510 --> 05:51.930
如果他有古怪  打爆他的头
If he gets squirrelly,put a bullet in his brain.

06:42.310 --> 06:44.570
你还真是稀客
You are a sight for sore eyes,my friend.

06:44.730 --> 06:45.860
少来了
Can the reunion.

06:46.030 --> 06:49.740
-迈克和林肯在哪  -他们处境不妙
-Where can I find Michael and Lincoln? -Apparently they're at dire straits.

06:49.910 --> 06:51.320
你聋了吗
Are you deaf?

06:51.450 --> 06:54.910
好着呢  刚才还听到你身上的硬币响
Unlikely, amigo, I just heard the dime drop on your sorry ass.

06:55.080 --> 06:59.250
看到我左肩旁的人吗
From the bench over my left shoulder,the gentleman in the Wayfarers.

07:00.750 --> 07:03.290
你脑袋还像在福克斯河一样不好使  
Like in Fox River,you never thought things through.

07:03.420 --> 07:07.380
告诉我要帮那兄弟俩的人是谁
You're gonna name the friend who said he'd show up and help out the brothers.

07:07.510 --> 07:10.970
把莎拉的手机给我  不然我打破你的脸
No, you're gonna hand Sara's phone or I'll break your face.

07:11.130 --> 07:14.180
说我是聋子  我看你是瞎子
You accuse me of being deaf,you're the one who's gone blind.

07:14.350 --> 07:17.810
那家伙可是公司一流的杀手
The man's a Company operative-trained assassin.

07:22.190 --> 07:23.480
伙计  你好啊
What's up, Jethro?

07:33.280 --> 07:35.830
我们可不是在福克斯河了  T-Bag  走吧
We're a long way from Fox River,T-Bag. Let's go.

07:40.330 --> 07:42.160
我拿到唐克雷蒂的电话了
Yeah, I got Tancredi's phone.

07:42.330 --> 07:45.330
往一个号码打了很多次
There's a bunch of calls made to a single number.

07:45.460 --> 07:47.340
应该是迈克的号
I think it's Michael's.

07:53.260 --> 07:55.680
他有糖尿病吗  是否忘了吃药
Is he diabetic? Medication he may have missed?

07:55.850 --> 07:58.010
不清楚  他是不是装的
I have no idea.Any chance he's faking it?

07:58.180 --> 07:59.770
不是  瞳孔放大
No, pupils are dilated.

07:59.930 --> 08:02.560
他需要CT透视  心电图和胸部X光
He needs a head CT stat,EKG and a chest x-ray.

08:02.730 --> 08:05.650
可能是脑淤血或心脏病
May have bled into his brain or had a heart attack.

08:05.810 --> 08:09.150
弗朗哥  仓库里不仅有斯科菲尔德和布鲁斯
Franco. It wasn’t just Scofield and Burrows.

08:09.320 --> 08:12.030
还有赛尔夫
This is the team that Self had at the warehouse.

08:13.280 --> 08:14.490
前联邦探员
Former federal agent.

08:14.660 --> 08:16.620
赛尔夫干了些不法勾当
Yeah, Self was into something nasty.

08:17.950 --> 08:19.580
赛尔夫  能听到吗
Agent Self, can you hear me?

08:19.740 --> 08:21.540
弗朗哥探员  我们要把他转移
Agent Franco, we have to move him.

08:21.710 --> 08:23.290
斯科菲尔德和布鲁斯在哪
Where are Scofield and Burrows?

08:23.460 --> 08:25.330
我们要走了
We're going now.

08:26.880 --> 08:29.550
等等  他的手动了  他能听见
Wait, his finger moved.He can hear me.

08:30.130 --> 08:32.260
赛尔夫探员  你能帮助我们吗
Agent Self, can you help us?

08:33.340 --> 08:34.720
他哪都不能去
He's not going anywhere.

08:37.050 --> 08:38.640
迈克  计划是什么
Michael, what's the plan?

08:38.810 --> 08:40.140
我们能相信谁
Who do we trust?

08:40.310 --> 08:42.310
没有人
No one.

08:42.480 --> 08:43.850
我们别无选择
We're out of options.

08:46.860 --> 08:48.400
我们应该把它毁了
Then maybe we destroy it.

08:49.820 --> 08:51.480
别无选择吗
Is that it?

08:51.610 --> 08:52.990
穷途末路了吗
Is that where we're at?

08:54.570 --> 08:57.030
如果将军决定报复应该怎么办
What if the general decides to retaliate?

08:57.200 --> 08:59.450
即使我们给了他  他也会的
He will even if we give it to him.

08:59.580 --> 09:01.910
我们可以把它弄碎  烧了
We can crush it, incinerate it.

09:02.660 --> 09:04.000
扔到海里
Throw in the ocean.

09:04.160 --> 09:06.870
-都行  -阿历克斯
-All three sound good.-Alex?

09:11.760 --> 09:13.170
好吧
All right.

09:14.260 --> 09:16.130
就这么决定了
Then it's decided.

09:20.010 --> 09:21.720
喂
Hello?

09:21.890 --> 09:23.970
你好  迈克
Hello, Michael.

09:24.890 --> 09:26.190
凯勒曼
Kellerman.

09:28.770 --> 09:30.980
你可真不好找啊
You're a tough man to get ahold of.

09:39.450 --> 09:41.530
听说你死了
I heard you were dead.

09:41.700 --> 09:45.040
那些流言言过其实了
Those rumors were greatly exaggerated.

09:45.290 --> 09:47.370
我没有
No, I was, um...

09:47.540 --> 09:50.040
我被与公司的对着干的一个组织救了
...freed by a group working against the Company.

09:50.210 --> 09:52.920
你父亲成立的组织  我跟他们一起工作
The group founded by your father,I'm working with them.

09:53.090 --> 09:55.300
我从那时起就一直跟他们工作
Now I've been working with them ever since.

09:55.470 --> 09:58.010
可以帮我一把
Could have used a hand, Paul.

09:58.180 --> 09:59.550
我来了
Here I am.

09:59.720 --> 10:01.100
你拿到锡拉了吗
Do you have Scylla?

10:01.260 --> 10:02.550
你认为呢
What do you think?

10:02.720 --> 10:04.640
你拿到了
I think you do.

10:05.600 --> 10:08.600
我也知道警察和联邦局的人在找你
I also know that you're wanted by the police and the feds.

10:08.770 --> 10:11.940
现在说说将军和你母亲
Not to mention the general and your mother.

10:12.110 --> 10:13.820
她不成问题
She won't be a problem.

10:13.980 --> 10:16.940
今天5点钟有联合国的专员到迈阿密
There is a U.N. attaché who will be in Miami today at 5:00...

10:17.110 --> 10:18.820
从你那里拿走锡拉
...to receive Scylla from you.

10:18.990 --> 10:20.660
就这些吗
Is that so?

10:20.820 --> 10:24.120
他是联合国秘书长的首席顾问
He's chief counsel to the secretary general of the United Nations.

10:24.290 --> 10:26.910
秘书长了解锡拉项目
The secretary has been briefed on the Scylla program.

10:27.080 --> 10:31.500
他决定承担起责任  你只要把它交出来
He's prepared to assume responsibility.All you have to do is deliver it.

10:31.630 --> 10:34.590
我们需要摆脱将军
We need to stop the general from coming after our families.

10:34.710 --> 10:36.670
没问题  但你要安排这次见面
Fine, but you need to make this meeting.

10:36.840 --> 10:39.260
我为什么要相信你
Why should I trust a word coming from your mouth?

10:39.430 --> 10:43.100
一旦交出锡拉  你们的罪行就会一笔勾消
Once Scylla is delivered,your slate is wiped clean.

10:43.850 --> 10:44.890
你们所有人
All of you.

10:45.600 --> 10:46.770
你会自由
You're free.

10:47.350 --> 10:49.140
那不是答案
That's not an answer, Paul.

10:50.480 --> 10:53.610
毫不夸张地说  我猜你知道你拿的东西
I assume you know that what you have can--

10:53.770 --> 10:58.030
可以让世界变得更好
And this is no exaggeration.--change the world for the better.

10:58.820 --> 11:01.700
你只需要交出它
All you have to do is deliver it.

11:01.870 --> 11:04.580
你不用相信我  你只需要
And you don't need to trust me,just trust the people...

11:04.700 --> 11:06.740
相信联合国的工作人员
...that worked at the United Nations.

11:11.420 --> 11:12.670
手机没电了
Phone died.

11:14.130 --> 11:16.710
-他还没有好转  -来  我们把他扶起来
-He's not getting any better. -Come on. Let's get him up.

11:16.880 --> 11:19.510
-我去拿点用品  -好
-I gotta get some supplies.-Okay.

11:26.390 --> 11:28.350
弗罗斯特探员和巴格威尔都没有音信
No word from Agent Frost or Bagwell.

11:28.520 --> 11:32.230
那个滑头  要是他擅离职守  我活剥了他
That simpering little rat.If he's AWOL, I'll skin him alive.

11:32.400 --> 11:36.570
他不可能搞定弗罗斯特  他可能被抓或者死了
No way he got over on Frost,he's captured. Or dead.

11:36.690 --> 11:39.440
就是说我们暴露了
So we're exposed here.

11:40.280 --> 11:42.030
就这么结束了吗
This is the end.

11:42.530 --> 11:44.030
真是凄惨啊
Whimpering.

11:44.200 --> 11:47.740
我们可以撤走等待东山再起
There's no shame in retreating to regroup, sir.

11:48.330 --> 11:51.620
那可没那么简单
That, son, is a tremendous load.

11:54.710 --> 11:56.210
喂
Yeah.

11:59.590 --> 12:02.170
塔台发现林肯·布鲁斯的手机信号
Lincoln Burrows' phone.Pinged to cell tower downtown.

12:02.340 --> 12:03.380
我们找到他的位置了
We have his location.

12:03.550 --> 12:05.470
那你还愣着干嘛
Then what are you doing here?

12:14.940 --> 12:16.110
是
Yeah.

12:16.730 --> 12:18.230
好
Okay.

12:21.110 --> 12:22.440
是凯勒曼
And that was Kellerman.

12:22.610 --> 12:25.490
这个阿拉巴马拖车男干的好事
This Alabama trailer trash has been making good.

12:25.660 --> 12:27.620
你投奔了克兰兹将军
You hooked up with General Krantz.

12:27.740 --> 12:30.830
-管你什么事  光头  -将军现在在哪
-What is it to you, rug head? -Well, where is the general now?

12:31.000 --> 12:34.710
跟你爹在一个地方  没人知道
Same place as your daddy.Location unknown.

12:44.550 --> 12:48.390
还记得排队等饭那一天吗
Do you remember that day we were in the chow line?

12:48.560 --> 12:50.220
在福克斯河
Fox River.

12:50.390 --> 12:52.810
你对我的侮辱
You made that off-handed comment to me.

12:52.980 --> 12:55.100
我相信一定带了民族色彩
I believe it had a racial bent to it.

12:55.270 --> 12:56.480
说对了
Yeah.

12:56.650 --> 12:58.480
还记得你脱臼的下巴吗
Do you remember your broken jaw?

13:00.110 --> 13:03.860
现在赶快想出点事关生死的正经事
Now, just imagine what I can do to you now with something real on the line.

13:04.030 --> 13:05.400
比如
Such as?

13:05.570 --> 13:09.030
我们想要索菲、L.J.和帕姆·马宏安全
We want safety for Sofia, L.J.and Pam Mahone.

13:09.370 --> 13:11.740
也就是说我们需要知道将军的位置
That means we need the general's location.

13:11.910 --> 13:14.250
我会有什么好处
-What's in it for me?

13:14.410 --> 13:17.210
我们把锡拉交出
If we take Scylla to the place it's supposed to be...

13:17.380 --> 13:19.380
会有一个赦免名单
...there'll be an immunity list.

13:19.540 --> 13:20.590
可以有你的名字
You could be on it.

13:20.750 --> 13:24.470
我的阵营虽然稍占劣势
No, where I'm sitting,I'll be momentarily compromised.

13:24.630 --> 13:27.680
但你们站错队营了  斯科菲尔德搞不定的
You're backing the wrong horse.Scofield cannot pull this out.

13:27.800 --> 13:30.470
我们把他交给将军  我们一辈子就不用愁了
